      <title>中国房地产股因刺激计划而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国房地产开发商的股价周一上涨，因市场猜测本周可能会出台更多刺激措施，旨在清理库存、促进销售和取消购房限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:47:49 GMT</pubDate>
